Certainly! Here are some frequently asked questions (FAQs) regarding balayage hair color and salon services at Code Hair in Dubai:

What is Balayage, and why is it so popular?

Balayage is a hair coloring technique where highlights are hand-painted onto the hair for a natural, sun-kissed look. It's popular because it creates soft, blended color that grows out beautifully with minimal maintenance.
How long does a balayage appointment at Code Hair typically take?

The duration of a balayage appointment can vary depending on the complexity of the desired look and the current condition of your hair. On average, it can take anywhere from 2 to 4 hours.
Is balayage suitable for all hair types and lengths?

Yes, one of the benefits of balayage is its versatility. It can be tailored to suit different hair types, lengths, and textures, from short bobs to long layers.
